根据选举法，投票率需要达到33％，赢得过半选票即可当选总统。如果无人过半，依法在40日内举行第二轮选举，由第一轮选举得票前两位的候选人参加。<ref name=bbc-qa>{{cite news|title=Q&A: Uzbek presidential election|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/7148442.stm|accessdate=2016-04-20|agency=BBC|date=2007-12-23|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827103724/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/7148442.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月24日晨，[[乌兹别克斯坦中央选举委员会|乌兹别克斯坦中央选举委员会]]公布初步计票结果，[[卡里莫夫|卡里莫夫]]获得88.1％的选票，赢得大选。<ref>{{cite news|title=Islam Karimov receives 88.1% votes at presidential elections|url=http://uza.uz/en/programs/the-year-of-the-healthy-child-/islam-karimov-receives-881-votes-at-presidential-elections-24.12.2007-142/|accessdate=2016-04-20|agency=UzA|date=2007-12-24|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160420114427/http://uza.uz/en/programs/the-year-of-the-healthy-child-/islam-karimov-receives-881-votes-at-presidential-elections-24.12.2007-142/|archive-date=2016-04-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2008年1月16日，卡里莫夫在首都[[塔什干|塔什干]]议会上下两院联席会议上宣誓就职。<ref>{{cite news|title=卡里莫夫宣誓就任乌兹别克斯坦新一任总统|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-01/17/content_7433436.htm|accessdate=2016-04-20|agency=新华网|date=2008-01-17|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305191820/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-01/17/content_7433436.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 评价 ==
[[欧安组织|欧安组织]]认为选举根本达不到欧安组织对民主的标准，对投票率的真实性推出质疑。欧安组织表示，因为选举没有真正的反对派，欧安组织没有必要派出太多观察员监督选举，所以只派了很小的团队前往乌兹别克斯坦。<ref name=bbc-win>{{cite news|title=Uzbek president wins third term|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/7159292.stm|accessdate=2016-04-20|agency=BBC|date=2007-12-24|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305003355/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/7159292.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[上海合作组织|上海合作组织]]、[[独联体|独联体]]等组织对选举给以称赞，认为选举遵守乌兹别克斯坦选举法和相关法律，达到了国际标准，实现了公开、透明、自由、民主。<ref>{{cite news|title=卡里莫夫再次当选乌兹别克斯坦总统|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2007-12/24/content_7306275.htm|accessdate=2016-04-20|agency=新华网|date=2007-12-24|archive-date=2008-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080103095036/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2007-12/24/content_7306275.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

